of different races and backgrounds.

115
00:07:28.980 --> 00:07:31.150
People who saw the world differently than
me.

116
00:07:31.150 --> 00:07:33.820
Who had different lived experiences than me.

117
00:07:33.820 --> 00:07:36.669
Because I got to escape to Hogwarts.

118
00:07:36.669 --> 00:07:39.500
Where being different didn’t mean you were
bad.

119
00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:42.650
Where being weird meant you were special,
not deviant.

120
00:07:42.650 --> 00:07:48.220
Where students of different races and nationalities
came together to bring down a villain hellbent

121
