I had my mind forced open to the fact that

125
00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:07.880
people who are different from me are not less
than me.

126
00:08:07.880 --> 00:08:10.699
Something I appreciated when I got to film
school and was surrounded by the types of

127
00:08:10.699 --> 00:08:14.540
