up until then.

128
00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:16.680
And I thanked Rowling for that.

129
00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:21.680
She helped this lonely gay kid feel not so
alone, that there was a group of people out

130
00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:24.300
there, somewhere, who would accept me.

131
00:08:24.300 --> 00:08:29.160
Who would welcome me in and make me feel like
a part of something bigger than just my small

132
00:08:29.160 --> 00:08:31.030
town.

133
00:08:31.030 --> 00:08:34.399
And I thanked her for that by spending as
much money on Harry Potter merchandise as

134
00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:35.399
