between Dumbledore and Grindlewald, something

150
00:09:22.911 --> 00:09:28.240
Rowling had confirmed after the release of
the final Harry Potter book.

151
00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:31.820
And then the director said we wouldn’t be
getting it in this movie and then the movie

152
00:09:31.820 --> 00:09:34.940
