158
00:09:49.790 --> 00:09:50.960
Movie 5.

159
00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:57.380
Because that way you’d be less likely to
lose the family audience throughout the series.”

160
00:09:57.380 --> 00:10:02.190
Nevermind that the script for Crimes of Grindlewald
was a disaster that absolutely reeked of first

161
00:10:02.190 --> 00:10:03.190
draft sickness.

162
00:10:03.190 --> 00:10:06.960
But I defended the movie and Rowling online
to no end.

163
00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:11.420
I spent hours figuring out how they could
confirm the relationship between Grindlewald

164
00:10:11.420 --> 00:10:17.480
and Dumbledore in some physical way that could
retain the PG-13 rating, and be easily removable

165
00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:19.620
for markets like China and Russia.

166
00:10:19.620 --> 00:10:26.120
I was invested in convincing other people
that they were wrong to criticize her.

167
00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:29.110
That she was playing the game as best she
could.

168
00:10:29.110 --> 00:10:32.120
After it was a box office disappointment,
I made the argument that it should go to a

169
00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:35.060
