189
00:11:51.550 --> 00:11:56.020
So, of course, I bought each set immediately
upon release.

190
00:11:56.020 --> 00:12:03.990
All the while defending her to gay friends
but, keeping quiet about her to my trans friends.

191
00:12:03.990 --> 00:12:10.750
Underneath my adoration for her I was starting
to feel… embarrassed.

192
00:12:10.750 --> 00:12:14.770
But it was easy enough to just keep buying
the merchandise, because the lego was being

193
00:12:14.770 --> 00:12:19.390
