TERFS like Maya Forstater and the shit completely

204
00:13:01.900 --> 00:13:03.610
hit the fan.

205
00:13:03.610 --> 00:13:08.840
When some of her followers criticized the
tweet as being off-color or even possibly

206
00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:11.930
transphobic Rowling responded by saying:

207
00:13:11.930 --> 00:13:13.460
“Dress however you please.

208
00:13:13.460 --> 00:13:15.270
Call yourself whatever you like.

209
00:13:15.270 --> 00:13:18.790
