218
00:13:49.040 --> 00:13:52.920
And out came the “If sex isn’t real”
argument.

219
00:13:52.920 --> 00:13:56.010
This is something that TERFs love to do.

220
00:13:56.010 --> 00:13:57.300
Equate sex and gender.

221
00:13:57.300 --> 00:14:01.410
Either because their ignorant of the difference,
too dumb to tell, or just assholes.

222
00:14:01.410 --> 00:14:03.810
Essentially, sex is biological in nature.

223
00:14:03.810 --> 00:14:07.130
