764
00:48:43.449 --> 00:48:45.789
People were telling their own stories in the
world.

765
00:48:45.789 --> 00:48:47.339
Creating their own characters.

766
00:48:47.339 --> 00:48:50.559
Adding to the mythology.

767
00:48:50.559 --> 00:48:56.819
And a whole lot of the people behind those
new stories were queer and trans.

768
00:48:56.819 --> 00:49:00.859
People who understood that Rowling couldn’t
include people like us in the initial books

769
00:49:00.859 --> 00:49:05.779
because of the then existing UK law that said
books with LGBT characters weren’t allowed

770
00:49:05.779 --> 00:49:08.180
in children’s libraries.

771
00:49:08.180 --> 00:49:13.519
So we assumed that was the only reason we
weren’t there, and many of us created out

772
00:49:13.519 --> 00:49:16.009
own stories to fill in the gaps.

773
00:49:16.009 --> 00:49:21.660
Creating new characters to exist right alongside
Harry, Ron, and Hermione.

774
00:49:21.660 --> 00:49:22.660
And why wouldn’t we?

775
00:49:22.660 --> 00:49:29.109
In 2014 JK Rowling stated, very clearly, that
gay, lesbian, bi, AND transgender students

776
00:49:29.109 --> 00:49:32.109
