783
00:49:58.170 --> 00:50:06.849
Until she went out of her way to remove that
last shadow of a doubt that so many of us

784
00:50:06.849 --> 00:50:07.849
clung to.

785
00:50:07.849 --> 00:50:10.390
And it sucks.

786
00:50:10.390 --> 00:50:12.660
I hate it.

787
00:50:12.660 --> 00:50:13.989
I hate that I defended her.

788
00:50:13.989 --> 00:50:16.900
I hate that I ignored her growing transphobia.

789
00:50:16.900 --> 00:50:21.199
But most of all, I hate that I had to.

790
00:50:21.199 --> 00:50:27.109
I hate that she put me and so many fans, gay,
straight, bi, cis, trans, non-binary…

791
00:50:27.109 --> 00:50:31.819
That she put us in the position of HAVING
to ignore her ignorant and potentially dangerous

792
00:50:31.819 --> 00:50:32.819
comments.

793
00:50:32.819 --> 00:50:37.959
Because she had helped us form our identities
as accepting, loving, people.

794
00:50:37.959 --> 00:50:42.569
The ones who would help the first years at
Hogwarts feel comfortable in their new home.

795
00:50:42.569 --> 00:50:46.410
No matter where they came from, what they
looked like, or what dormitory they slept

796
00:50:46.410 --> 00:50:47.410
in.

797
00:50:47.410 --> 00:50:52.259
Over the course of just a few short years
Joanne Rowling went from being the most tolerant,

798
00:50:52.259 --> 00:50:56.900
accepting, loving professor at Hogwarts…
to She Who Must Not Be Named.

799
00:50:56.900 --> 00:51:02.700
And while doing so she created her own hoard
of TERFY death eaters to go along with her,

800
00:51:02.700 --> 00:51:06.400
leaving the rest of us heartbroken at the
betrayal, and trying to figure out what to

801
00:51:06.400 --> 00:51:08.240
do next.

802
00:51:08.240 --> 00:51:11.540
Do we cut Harry Potter out of our lives.

803
00:51:11.540 --> 00:51:12.920
Or just it’s creator?

804
00:51:12.920 --> 00:51:16.410
Do we have to let go of something that made
us feel so happy and safe?

805
00:51:16.410 --> 00:51:19.319
Or can we just let go of her?

806
00:51:19.319 --> 00:51:21.749
Can there be Harry Potter without JK Rowling?

807
00:51:21.749 --> 00:51:22.749
