839
00:53:19.150 --> 00:53:23.130
No modern author has had the reach of JK Rowling.

840
00:53:23.130 --> 00:53:26.109
The cultural permeability.

841
00:53:26.109 --> 00:53:30.219
Harry Potter has sold over 500 million copies.

842
00:53:30.219 --> 00:53:33.619
Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone
