843
00:53:33.619 --> 00:53:37.209
With the other six books in the series all
landing within the top 20 bestselling books

844
00:53:37.209 --> 00:53:38.209
of all time.

845
00:53:38.209 --> 00:53:39.209
Rowling is the only author to have more than
one book in that top twenty, and she’s got

846
00:53:39.209 --> 00:53:40.209
seven.

