862
00:54:40.980 --> 00:54:46.150
That Molly Weasly was a loving and accepting
mother figure.

863
00:54:46.150 --> 00:54:52.329
That Professor McDonagall was a teacher they
wish they’d had to talk to.

864
00:54:52.329 --> 00:54:56.259
