00:56:06.950 --> 00:56:09.999
Hermione still fights for the rights of the
oppressed, even though they’re different

885
00:56:09.999 --> 00:56:12.670
from her.

886
00:56:12.670 --> 00:56:18.449
Molly Weasely is still the mother figure that
will hug you and care for you, no matter what.

887
00:56:18.449 --> 00:56:22.789
Sirius is still the godfather that will make
you laugh, and put his life on the line for

888
00:56:22.789 --> 00:56:25.229
you.

889
00:56:25.229 --> 00:56:27.349
Dobby is still the devoted friend.

890
00:56:27.349 --> 00:56:30.059
McGonagall still the caring teacher.

891
00:56:30.059 --> 00:56:33.719
Hagrid still the father figure that will guide
you through the dark.

892
00:56:33.719 --> 00:56:38.949
They’re all still there within the pages
and on the screen.

893
00:56:38.949 --> 00:56:43.690
Inside a worn paperback or old DVD you got
as a kid or a teenager.

894
00:56:43.690 --> 00:56:50.219
And on September 1, you can still return to
Hogwarts without putting a single Knut, sickle,

895
00:56:50.219 --> 00:56:54.019
or galleon in Rowling’s pocket.

896
00:56:54.019 --> 00:56:56.460
Rowling did her job.

897
00:56:56.460 --> 00:56:57.789
She wrote the books.

898
00:56:57.789 --> 00:57:01.069
But They’re yours now.

899
00:57:01.069 --> 00:57:02.609
Always.